TetriNET X Modern

This project is an update of the classic tetrinetx server to be
supported by new linux distributions and C compiler versions.

The job is basically review the code and replace the old varargs.h
to stdarg.h and some bug fixes.

This code was built using Ubuntu 20.04.1 LTS and it was developed
using Visual Studio Code running in Windows 10, integrated with
WSL (Windows Subsystem for Linux) to compile and run the code
in the native environment.

This job is under progress and it is beign done by
